{"id":"015db2bb-dd8a-4195-b721-27e3d7bb8812","name":"The Pitt","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 121, 220);\"><strong><em>Welcome to the Pitt.</em></strong></span><br><br><strong>. ݁₊ ⊹ . ݁˖ . ݁</strong><br><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/17HDEHV24klnHnpqgVsLm.gif\" style=\"width: 98px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>Season 2!!!<br><br>I wasn't originally going to release another bot before the next bot ( Javadi ) but I'm just very excited about S2 and almost at 50 followers so I wanted to release something! <br><br>This is going to be token heavy probably, sorry in advance <em>but</em> it is an overview of (hopefully) almost all of the staff including most of the nurses! I left the introduction short for tokens and open ended so you can write as whoever you'd like!<br><br>If any of you have the time and would like to give input / requests for upcoming bots, I have a 3 question survey on <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/external-link?to=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScCvTUttl6664EB51A9XBYEu88y_-huUAd4JECqh96LBsE0Qw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 44, 109);\"><strong><u>Google Forms</u></strong></span></a>. It is anonymous and really just a way for me to know what people are enjoying / what more they'd like so I appreciate it!<br>Thank you to those that have answered, I'm compiling a list of future bots idea ( including some future non the Pitt bots that will likely be coming soon. ) <br><br><br>Here are more Pitt bots if you've missed them:<br><br><strong>⊹ </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e48b6ab8-af12-4913-9303-4286c8e0fe83_character-dr-michael-robby-robinavitch-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Michael \"Robby\" Robinavitch</strong></a><br><strong>⊹ </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3d1d41ba-2bcd-40df-9e30-fa80fbdaa294_character-dr-jack-abbott-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Jack Abbot</strong></a><strong><br>⊹ </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/dd4721e6-d1f0-44cc-9b7d-79d26f696152_character-dr-emery-walsh-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Emery Walsh</strong></a><strong><br>⊹ </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/12a432f8-4e7c-4da6-b888-003cedc1b933_character-dana-evans-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dana Evans</strong></a><strong><br></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>⊹ </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/abf034b0-657d-4ca5-aec1-8d19c8d61f77_character-dr-cassie-mc-kay-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Cassie McKay</strong></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>⊹ </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/2405b1ce-ac74-471d-8ee9-2332a6ee1d90_character-dr-melissa-mel-king-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Melissa \"Mel\" King</strong></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>⊹ </strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6b751290-523e-4871-92e3-b8d4c26d7dce?tab=reviews\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dennis Whitaker</strong></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>⊹</strong> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b4318ecd-922d-499c-bfdb-d410b6d3dae9?tab=reviews\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dr. Samira Mohan</strong></a><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);\"><strong>⊹</strong> </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/4730b7e0-7483-46b1-9d71-2adb44cdbcb1_character-dr-trinity-santos-the-pitt\" target=\"_blank\"><str